OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FClarks agrees to mediation 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fin fire-and-rehire strike  
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The shoe retailer Clarks has agreed to 
OL,6, allow mediators to help resolve a      
OL,7, strike at its warehouse in Street,     
OL,8, Somerset.                              
OL,10,FThe conciliation service Acas confirmed
OL,11,Fthat it is in contact with the company 
OL,12,Fand the union about arranging talks.   
OL,14,FStaff at the warehouse have been on    
OL,15,Fstrike since 4 October over pay and    
OL,16,Fconditions.                            
OL,18,FClarks wants the workers to accept new 
OL,19,Fcontracts, which would cut pay for a   
OL,20,Fnumber of long-serving employees.      
